{"tid":228053,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"[女同AV]  張敏疑似表白周慧敏 兩大女神要出櫃？","createTime":"2017-05-03T15:16:49.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-04T07:55:17.000Z","uid":22876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"dc3f5f48d4a2e5615f07d01ef1a251aab90af72c","tid":228053,"uid":22876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T15:16:49.000Z","msg":"【博聞社】5月3日晚9:08，張敏在微博髮長文，深情感言：「請許我守住輪迴與你同在於雲淡風輕里，銘刻深情。」並配上自己與周慧敏的照片，讓無數粉絲浮想聯翩。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/C-6SqKRXUAAAjgV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FC-6SqKRXUAAAjgV.jpg&h=5d1240be&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://bowenpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/10-1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbowenpress.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F05%2F10-1.jpg&h=5958d6e0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n張敏微博原文：<br />\n<br />\n這一世，你安守著我，無約無期<br />\n<br />\n看繁花棲滿枝，聽風推浪，只許一肩<br />\n<br />\n這一世，榮華有你，落寞與你<br />\n<br />\n乍見，便是此生的共勉<br />\n<br />\n於四季裡，描摹彼此生命的輪廓<br />\n<br />\n此一生，僅一念<br />\n<br />\n重逢是我，歸來有你<br />\n<br />\n以三千溫婉，揮淚笑對<br />\n<br />\n願將這份守候，繪一幅清淺的水墨於<br />\n<br />\n濃處相惜，在淡處相念<br />\n<br />\n遠近相宜，便是你我恰好的相伴<br />\n<br />\n若可，請許我守住輪迴與你同在<br />\n<br />\n於雲淡風輕裡，銘刻深情<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c38711d88c1d655af29c5c876ed67c5f1da0173","tid":228053,"uid":100442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T15:18:49.000Z","msg":"樓主幾時比狗屌？"},{"pid":"2968fad07e601968b8f73d3256e2116aabee13a1","tid":228053,"uid":30574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T15:18:51.000Z","msg":"日J夜J既女神s原來鍾意磨豆腐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e58412cbe851b00e40f1577e51245e7acd9805bb",